Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等水在沙槽里积起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢水倾泻而出的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着水决堤 得以解放 奔流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沙槽里蓄满的能量爆发开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都会动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玉木真理小姐 都已经中午啰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我好像做了个噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈举着条湿毛巾往我脸上盖 想谋杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那还真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我昨天有叫你收拾房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上高中想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}写日记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旷一次课
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来场说走就走的旅行
