Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&HDAE3DA&\pos(670,548)}（试试看～怎么样）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我打算先去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后来场说走就走的旅行 随心漂泊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Enjoy your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我要逃学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是要请假逃学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得这点想法挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道小理 你没逃过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小惠 你逃过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有人没逃过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别用那种眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你试过说走就走的旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那倒是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么知道我要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会想些什么 我还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种旅行 一个人才有意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就在车站的厕所换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是大海耶 大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 会被发现是群马县人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.94,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※群马县是日本少有的内陆县。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}姊姊你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么早就要出门啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那包包是要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟朋友借了运动服还没还
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又借了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用担心 我打过电话给老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}学你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你得在外住一晚 我会跟你统一说词的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用担心 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在厕所换上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搭上与学校反方向的火车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人逃离平时的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}踏上说走就走的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去一个陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面下雨了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我觉得 逃学是不好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没有想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有啊 有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}京都 冲绳 北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怎么没去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飞机说不定会坠毁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新干线说不定会爆炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陨石说不定会从天而降？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怎么没走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我总是会这样
