Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想加社团的时候 想学东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想挑战名校的入学考试的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都在事到临头前退怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦尝试没有做过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总会想不顺利的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想要失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会不会后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每到最后关头总会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得这也不是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:17.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\1c&H242D2B&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz346.2\move(596,274,596,270,0,5754)}门禁前会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:17.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\1c&H353939&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz344.3\move(70,388,44,384,0,5754)}我做了常吃的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最讨厌自己这一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次要不要一起出去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 你东西掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 总共多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}数了一下 正好100万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100万！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你拿来干嘛 要送去警局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家吓到忘记了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真会找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦 我认真的 真的是吓呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且掉了这个信封的人 好像是穿我们学校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几年级的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是瞄到她的背影一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发型和那边那位很像 大概是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味道很香 润丝的香味？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这点线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 头发那么长的人大概不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去看看一年级的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}静不下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100万…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100万元…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100万…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 其实昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 我没骗你 真的是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}写这本书的人是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前是南极观测员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我上国中的时候 她突然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后没找到人 基本上也没什么遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想去找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极吗？你能去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家也是这种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外婆 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老师 学长 还有邻居
